properties.name: Solano County Green Valley
properties.approved_maps: (1) “Mt. George Quadrangle, California”, 7.5 minute series (1968); and (2) “Cordelia Quadrangle, California”, 7.5 minute series (1968).
properties.boundary_description: (1) From the beginning point, the boundary runs in a southerly direction along the Napa/Solano County border to State Road 12; (2) Thence east along State Road 12 to where it intersects with Interstate 80; (3) Thence southwest on Interstate 80 to where it intersects with the Southern Pacific Railroad track; (4) Thence in an easterly direction along the Southern Pacific Railroad track to where it intersects with range line “R3W/R2W”; (5) Thence due north on range line “R3W/R2W” to where it intersects with the Solano County/Napa County line; (6) Thence due west along the Solano County/Napa County line to the point of beginning.
